---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="Leter privacy policy." />
    <title>Privacy | leter.net</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-surface">
      <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-muted hover:text-text">‚Üê Back to home</a>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: February 15, 2026</p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-muted">
          <p>
            This policy explains how leter.net currently handles data for this invite-only
            initiative.
          </p>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">1. Data collected on this site</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              This landing site is static. We do not currently provide account signup or mailbox
              storage directly through leter.net.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">2. Mail routing disclosure</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Mail routing and mailbox provisioning currently use
              <a
                class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2"
                href="https://forwardemail.net"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
              >
                Forward Email
              </a>
              (zero-knowledge provider). Leter does not currently operate mailbox-level storage
              directly.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">3. Operational logs</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Standard infrastructure and access logs may be processed by Lewsion for reliability,
              abuse prevention, and security.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">4. Roadmap notice</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              The roadmap includes migration toward sovereign infrastructure. If data practices
              change, this policy will be updated before those changes take effect.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-text">5. Contact</h2>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Privacy inquiries: <span class="text-text">privacy@leter.net</span> (placeholder)
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
